# Deployment and DevOps (rule)

**Full workflow, env lists, CI mapping, and checklists** live in the project skill [dapp-deployment-devops](mdc:.cursor/skills/dapp-deployment-devops/SKILL.md). Load that skill for releases, deploys, and pipeline work.

## File anchors

- **Ignition**: [backend/ignition/modules/](mdc:backend/ignition/modules/)
- **CI**: [.github/workflows/](mdc:.github/workflows/) (e.g. [ci-tests.yml](mdc:.github/workflows/ci-tests.yml))
- **Frontend build**: [frontend/next.config.mjs](mdc:frontend/next.config.mjs), [frontend/package.json](mdc:frontend/package.json)
- **Networks / RPC alignment**: [frontend/src/lib/wagmi.config.ts](mdc:frontend/src/lib/wagmi.config.ts)
